name: Jenna Wolfe
description:
Funny, she doesn't look Jamaican...

Stereotypes, right? Well, she is! Jenna Wolfe, who you might known from The Today Show (and those of us in the New York area remember from the MSG Network) is a bonafide Jamaican! She was born on the island, where her father owned a leather factory.

Funny, she doesn't look Haitian...

Stereotypes, right? Well, she is! Jenna Wolfe was actually raised in Haiti, spending her formative childhood years there.

Funny, she doesn't look Jewish....

What are you talking about? She definitely looks Jewish! Stereotypes, right!
